title: Prepare Android Studio migration: Fix XML headers
message:
Prepare Android Studio migration: Fix XML headers

Android Studio will convert XML:
* Replace UTF-8 with utf-8 in the header
* Use double quotes instead of single ones in the header
* Remove the Byte Order Mark

Doing that in advance will allow Git to find back the files after they will
get moved in the new structure and preserve history.

title: Fix NPE when updating status icon
message:
Fix NPE when updating status icon

The ImageView was initially removed from the parent to hide it, but then when
we try to get a reference to it again to change the drawable, it's NULL.

Instead of removing the view, hide it using View.GONE which has the desired
effect (no space taken on the layout).

title: [issue #59] Modified voice recording behavior. Voice recording can now be…
message: [issue #59] Modified voice recording behavior. Voice recording can now be started during track logger view by either pressing DPAD_CENTER for 1 second or by pressing HEADSETHOOK. Additionally voice recording duration preference has been extended to allow 10, 20 and 30 seconds of recording time.
